        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Calculated based on literature value and estimates. The total production of graphical paper in the world in 2007 is 1.5E11kg (http://www.statista.com/statistics/167107/production-volume-of-paper-by-type/, accessed 20130313). 

Based on data from Europe the treatment technology shares are assumed to be as follows;

28.7% of waste graphical paper is recycled
27.3% of waste graphical paper is incinerated
44.0% of waste graphical paper is landfilled</productionVolumeComment>
